OOC: yes, you can control as many characters that you can manage.  Good 
explanation as to how Megastorm survived, Kinger. Oh, and Megastorm cant have 
revenge because Deathsaurus is dead. The closest thing to having revenge 
would be to seek out the former Neocons, Falcon, Snare(both now in the 
Destrons), Jetstorm(in the Chosen Mafia) and Hellbat(in the Alliance).

:::Starscream:::

::He fires 25 shots from each gun at Nighteyes::
